p.k: Robin decides to become a cat so that Starfire will finally love him. / After being defeated due to poor leg strength Raven and the Titans work out their lower bodies and become the League of Legs. / When Beast Boy gets a stack of cash from the Tooth Fairy against Raven's advice the other Titans start knocking out their own teeth to get some of that sweet Tooth Fairy money. / A giant cocoon mysteriously appears in the Titans' living room and no one can find Beast Boy. / Tired of Robin's bland cooking the other Titans try their hand at spicing up their food.
